{"word":"Forgetting God","slug":"forgetting-god","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Forgetting God</b> A characteristic of the wicked<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=2&verse=17'>Pro 2:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=65&verse=11'>Isa 65:11</a><br/> Backsliders guilty of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=2&verse=32'>Jer 2:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=3&verse=21'>Jer 3:21</a><br/> Is forgetting His:<br/> - Covenant<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=4&verse=23'>Deu 4:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=38'>2Ki 17:38</a> <br/> - Works<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=78&verse=7'>Psa 78:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=78&verse=11'>Psa 78:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=106&verse=13'>Psa 106:13</a> <br/> - Benefits<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=103&verse=2'>Psa 103:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=106&verse=7'>Psa 106:7</a> <br/> - Word<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=12&verse=5'>Heb 12:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=1&verse=25'>Jas 1:25</a> <br/> - Law<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=119&verse=153'>Psa 119:153</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=119&verse=176'>Psa 119:176</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=4&verse=6'>Hos 4:6</a> <br/> - Church (1)<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=137&verse=5'>Psa 137:5</a> <br/> - Past deliverances<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=8&verse=34'>Jdg 8:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=78&verse=42'>Psa 78:42</a> <br/> - Powe